  "bodyHtml": "<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Jump to:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ol><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #2980b9;font-weight: bold;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><a href=\"#H1\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;\">What is the Visibility Boost? </a></span></strong></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #2980b9;font-weight: bold;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><a href=\"#H2\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;\">How would my business benefit from applying the Visibility Boost? </a></span></strong></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #2980b9;font-weight: bold;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><a href=\"#H3\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;\">Where can I find the Visibility Boost? </a></span></strong></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #2980b9;font-weight: bold;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><a href=\"#H4\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;\">How does the visibility work? </a></span></strong></li></ol>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><a id=\"H1\" target=\"_blank\"></a>What is Visibility Boost?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>The Visibility Boost </strong>is a new marketing tool that offers you extra visibility on Back Market &amp; on Google Shopping when you implement price drops. It’s available across select listings to ensure maximum visibility and traffic.</span></p>\n<h2></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><a id=\"H2\" target=\"_blank\"></a>How would my business benefit from Visibility Boost?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">By opting in, your eligible listings will appear across:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">The <strong>Great Deals</strong> page</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">The <strong>Product page</strong></span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;font-weight: bold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Google Shopping</span></strong></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">The <strong>Back Market app</strong></span></li></ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">A specific “price drop” tag will appear on your products on the customer-facing page. This increased exposure helps you drive more traffic and ultimately, more sales.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><a id=\"H3\" target=\"_blank\"></a>Where to find it?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">You can find the<strong> Visibility Boost </strong>on your <strong>Listings page</strong>, in the <strong>pricing strategy column.</strong> The tool suggests a discounted price. If you decide to apply that price, you’ll benefit from the Visibility Boost.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">It will only appear for eligible listings and be visible across approximately 5-10% of listings. Eligibility is intentionally limited to ensure strong and high-quality placement.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Please note:</strong> As a seller on Back Market, you are always free to set your own prices. The Visibility Boost is entirely optional and non-binding. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><a id=\"H4\" target=\"_blank\"></a>How does it work?</span></h2>\n<ol><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Go to your <strong>Back Office → Listings page</strong></span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Look for the <strong>pricing strategy column</strong></span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Select an eligible listing and apply the Visibility Boost</span></li></ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">The beta is <strong>live now</strong>; feel free to try it on an eligible listing and monitor the impact on your sales.</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><img src=\"/ssc/servlet/rtaImage?eid=ka0aT000000S9zd&amp;feoid=00N3X00000M5fJO&amp;refid=0EMaT00000JPduV\" alt=\"\" width=\"746\" height=\"252\" style=\"display: block;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;\"></img> </span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Updates: </span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">The eligible listings are updated every Monday.  </span></p>"
}